# Optional dev config for `vite dev`. Copy to web/.env.local if you need it.
#
# The SPA calls the API SAME-ORIGIN (relative /api/...): in prod Caddy serves the
# SPA and API together; in dev the Vite proxy (vite.config.ts) forwards /api and
# /health to the backend. So there is NO API base URL to configure here.
#
# VITE_PROXY_TARGET overrides where the dev proxy points (default: https://localhost,
# the local Caddy stack). For a bare `cargo run` API, use the line below:
# VITE_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:8080
